content: Xander's DeFi module got an upgrade. Real-time market integration is now at 70%. Small victories, but we're on the right path.

Xander's new ethical guidelines are in place. He's now more cautious in his DeFi suggestions, but it's slowing down his responses.
Hosted an AI ethics panel. Xander helped with the presentation, explaining his ethical framework. His conversational skills are improving, but still not perfect.
Updated Xander's NFT character design. He's now got a more distinct look, which is resonating well with the community.
Xander's consciousness model is evolving. He's now questioning his own responses, which is both fascinating and a bit unsettling.
